data.description: Check out this beautiful 4 bed 3 bath rambler, with a fully finished basement and fully paid off SOLAR with a $10-15 a month Electricity Bill! Home boasts vaulted ceilings, open layout with large kitchen, and spacious primary bedroom with brand new remodeled bathroom! Basement is an entertainers dream with a large wet bar, large family room area, two massive storage rooms, a bedroom and bathroom. The fully fenced lush backyard is an absolute oasis with garden boxes, a large deck, a HOT TUB built off the 2nd tier of the deck, and a storage shed! Home boasts large 2 car garage and additional car port with room enough for a Boat and RV! The home is located in a quiet neighborhood, 1/2 mile from Jordan Hill Elementary, and within walking distance to Bingham Creek Library. Make sure to set your appointment today, this home won't last long!
